title: Sweet Pain - Sweet Pain  (1969) [FLAC]
description:
Sweet Pain was a blues-session project of some members and ex-members of John Mayall's Bluesbreakers, Savoy Brown, the Aynsley Dunbar Retaliation, Alexis Korner's Blues Inc. and the Graham Bond Organisation.


Tracklist

	The Steamer 	
	Changin' Your Mind 	
	Rubbin' And Scrapin' 	
	Sick And Tired 	
	The Rooster Crows At Midnight 	
	Troubles Trouble 	
	Don't Break Down 	
	It's A Woman 	
	General Smit 	
	Trouble In Mind 	
	Song Of The Medusa 



Lineup:

Annette Brox - vocals
John O'Leary - harmonica
Keith Tilman - bass
Stuart Cowell - guitar
Dick Heckstall-Smith - saxophones
Sam Crozier - vocals, piano, pocket trumpet, 12 string guitar
Junior Dunn - drums
